      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Formal test sample characterization beyond what is documented in the FDA benchmark protocol is not required at MRL 2. FDA benchmark data provides sufficient sample documentation for this assessment level."
    },
